00:35:46.860 --> 00:35:50.770
investment in these kinds of
high-welfare operations, but

00:35:50.770 --> 00:35:52.550
not because there
isn't demand.

00:35:52.550 --> 00:35:55.020
That is, pretty much everybody
who's looking at investing in

00:35:55.020 --> 00:35:57.340
